{"tid":852991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蓬佩奧訪中 與王毅相互嚴厲責難","createTime":"2018-10-08T09:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T21:32:15.000Z","uid":13663,"like":96,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"754add709f8e4b65242bd35522579404d8b9bb32","tid":852991,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"中國和美國雙邊關係持續惡化之際，美國國務卿蓬佩奧和中國外長王毅今天會面，但一開始的氣氛就冷若冰霜，兩人相互嚴厲責難。王毅與蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）會面時說：「最近一段時間，美方在不斷升級對華貿易摩擦的同時，又在台灣等問題上採取了一系列損害中方權益的行為，並且無端指責中國的內外政策。」<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧向王毅表示：「針對你所描述的問題，我們基本上意見不同。我們對中國採取的行動極為擔憂。」蓬佩奧剛結束北韓訪問，他此行曾與北韓領導人金正恩會面。"},{"pid":"c3e879087914185c45b0667d90eed5a848ac8076","tid":852991,"uid":24853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:10:22.000Z","msg":"幾時先有習狗回應"},{"pid":"7e04298ff457b2ce8dbc902cc6b852b0466f1a22","tid":852991,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:15:14.000Z","msg":"正喇"},{"pid":"18c1705429fb4d6cbf59e8cd02bf25ba36910f2b","tid":852991,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Cold War"},{"pid":"c069bb816532c668089840ecc8357710b387d284","tid":852991,"uid":57554,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"一開波寒暄都冇就互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4bdb12d319173a9cf528ac1817566170ae2c1d3","tid":852991,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T09:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7839147a6c812032a8ab3d4472f77da55cd6f983","tid":852991,"uid":102096,"like":40,"